<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Climbs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The general price index of
Tehran Stock Exchange on Tuesday closed at 1511.90 points, up
1.17 points from Monday's closing.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,315,383 shares worth over 3.23 billion rials
(about 587,000 U.S. dollars) changed hands. The shares of 34
companies made gains while those of 17 others declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
