<HEADLINE> Guidi Wins Fourth Stage in Tour of Spain </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
MADRID, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Italian rider Fabrizio Guidi
won the 173.5-kilometer fourth stage of the Tour of Spain cycle
race, from Malaga to Granada on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Guidi also took over the race lead from Frenchman Laurent
Jalabert. 
</P>
