<HEADLINE> China Aiming to Dominate in Military Pentathlon Worlds </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 9 (Xinhua) -- China military pentathlon
team is aiming to dominate in the upcoming CISM 46th Military
Pentathlon World Championships at home.
</P>
<P>
China boost their chance to collect half of the six trophies
as the Democratic People's Republic of Korea (DPRK) pulled out of
the military sport +event on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The DPRK, who took the silver medals in both women's team and
individual divisions last year, are the winners of the women's
obstacles relay race and still hold the world record of this race.
</P>
<P>
"Women athletes who have better marks in obstacles relays are
priors to our selection for the competition," said Jiao
Liming,China's team leader.
</P>
<P>
China brought home the women's team and individual titles last
year in Sweden, and their domination in women's races is
unmovable after Koreans' pull-out.
</P>
<P>
"We have the potential to sweep the 1-2-3 finish in the
individual contest," Jiao added.
</P>
<P>
"But we'll meet powerful challenge from Brazil's men's team,"
Jiao said.
</P>
<P>
China won the men's team trophy, Debrus Cup, for the third
time in row last year and also the men's relay race, but Brazil's
Carlos Silva stole the individual champoinship.
</P>
<P>
"Brazil is the biggest obstacle for us to defending the Debrus
Cup,with Silva and veteran (Ribamar) Bandeira also their hopes
for the individual title," Jiao said.
</P>
<P>
Bandeira won the men's individual three times in 1990, 1991
and 1994.
</P>
<P>
Brazil's coach Helcio Botelho said, "We're better prepared for
the competition, and we're confident to beat China to win the
Debrus Cup."
</P>
<P>
"Silva is in a better form now than Bandeira, but both could
win the individual title. It all depends on the shooting,"
Botelho added.
</P>
<P>
"Besides Brazil, we have to keep eyes on other competitors,
like Syria and Russia," Jiao said.
</P>
<P>
Russia finished third last year behind China and Brazil in
Sweden.
</P>
<P>
"But Syria may be the surprise of the competition," Jiao
said."They didn't make any remarkable results in the pass years,
but they have the potential."
</P>
<P>
Jamal Hamadeh is the name Jiao mentioned as a dark horse in
the individual title chasing, who is still an unknown by now,
</P>
<P>
"If he (Hamadeh) manages to overcome his nervousness, he is
unbeatable."
</P>
<P>
The military sport gala will have the opening ceremony
tomorrow and the competition will start on Friday, with the
shooting competition the first contest of the seven-day event.
</P>
