<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Up 1.13 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, September 9(Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
(SET) index Wednesday gained 1.13 points from Tuesday to close at
213.98.
</P>
