<HEADLINE> Clinton, Sharif Discuss Regional Situation on Phone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
ISLAMABAD, September 9 (Xinhua) -- U.S. President Bill Clinton
called Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif Tuesday night and
discussed with him the regional situation in light of the latest
developments.
</P>
<P>
The two leaders exchanged views on measures to further
