<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, September 9 (Xinhua)-- Russian acting Prime Minister
Viktor Chernomyrdin Tuesday chaired a meeting on emergency
measures in the financial policy and instructed to prepare
normative documents dealing with customs and taxation problems.
</P>
<P>
The documents will allow to collect customs payments in foreign
currency and lift limits on the payment of customs dues in cash at
customs offices, the Itar-Tass news agency reported.
</P>
<P>
