lowering oil excise.
</P>
<P>
The Federal Tax Police Service has been instructed to comb
retail outlets since September 10 to prevent an unjustified price
rise.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, as many as 50 leading companies planned to transfer
their tax accounts to the Bank of Russia, the Federal Treasury,
the Savings Bank and the Vneshtorgbank for the sake of tax
collection and tax revenues of the federal budget. 
